Gunmen have kidnapped the Da Gwom Rwei of Vwang District in the Jos-South Local Government Area of Plateau State, HRH. Da Gyang Balak Gut. It was gathered that the monarch was abducted on Sunday night few meters from the gate of the National Institute for Policy and Strategic Studies, Kuru in Jos. File photo used to illustrate story. The incident is coming a few weeks after the abduction of another traditional ruler, Charles Mato, the Sum Pyem, and paramount ruler of Gindri, in Mangu Local Government Area of Plateau State. More details later